snippet.title: Mindcop Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pick up more clues:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mindcopgames/?modal=admin_todo_tour

Twitter: https://twitter.com/mindcopgames


Subscribe to the mailing list and get an exclusive digital poster:

https://mailchi.mp/5174e50055d4/mindcopsignup


This completely nonlinear detective game lets the player take over a murder case as the infamous mindcop. 

A grumpy police investigator with the ability to surf people's brainwaves to acquire otherwise hidden information.
